<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1063251" n="1"/>
<opener><lb/><salute>Viro Illustrissimo <abbr>atq.</abbr> Celeberrimo <rs type="person">Nicolao Bernoullio</rs>
  <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Sebastianus Checotius</rs>.</salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Inurbanus videar, Vir Clarissime, nisi, ubi me prim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>torum dierum occupationes sinunt, morem gessero postulatis tuis:
    <lb/>quod tamen d<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sto, efficiend<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> est pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea mihi, ut qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ante pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>posui explicem accuratius. Quod enim ego scripser<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> futurum, ut qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cumque
    <lb/>absolut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> temporum viriumque significationes attingantur rectis <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula> <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</abbr>
    <lb/>analoga quad<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> substitutione, e<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dem ips<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <del>[...]</del><add>Coor</add>dinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>ABC</formula>, per
    <lb/>quas semel confecta res fuerit, semper sint propositis conditionibus satisfa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ctur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>; his inqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> verbis tu prim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> notas nihil significari aliud, quam
    <lb/>quod in mea ad te primum missa <rs type="biblio">solutione</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dixeram; at id ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fect<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> est quod volebam, ut scilicet non aliquid afferrem novi, sed quidnam
    <lb/>in mea solutione a te adverti cuperem, commemorarem: Deinde ea verba
    <lb/><hi rend="u">quicumque affingatur valor lineis <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula></hi>, it<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> interpretaris; <hi rend="u">qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cumque
      <lb/>fuerit relatio inter <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula> <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c<supplied>.</supplied></abbr></hi>; at ego non <hi rend="u">quamcumque relation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></hi>, sed
    <lb/>unam, eandemque qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> semel statuta fuerit requiro, quoni<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> novos rectis
    <lb/><formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula> valores affingi <hi rend="u">analoga substitutione</hi> iubeo, ut propterea mutatis
    <lb/>licet quantitatibus, illar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ad invicem ratio non mutetur. Ut meam
    <lb/>igitur mentem tibi<supplied>,</supplied> <abbr>V.</abbr> <abbr>Cl.</abbr><supplied>,</supplied> plan<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> aperiam: Dico, per Curvilineum <formula>ABEC</formula>
    <lb/><figure/> (cuius absciss<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tempora, ordinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> autem vires exponant elapsis tempo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ribus convenientes) nihil aliud exhiberi, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter <hi rend="u">scalam</hi> quand<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
    <lb/><choice><orig>|</orig><reg>(</reg></choice>Architectonic<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> voce utar<choice><orig>|</orig><reg>)</reg></choice>, <hi rend="u">virium <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> tempor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>; videlicet analogi<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>,
      <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vires inter <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> tempora haberi debet, ad hoc ut <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> ipsa conditioni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bus positis satisfiat, non autem eorundem tempor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> aut virium
      <lb/>absolutam aliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> quantitatem, determinatamque mensur<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>.</hi> Hoc est; si
    <lb/>exponat <formula>AC</formula> tempus <abbr>ex. g.<hi><choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></hi></abbr> hor<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> unius; <formula>BA</formula> vim, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> dicere lubet libr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> unius,
    <lb/>(obvi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> alicuius imaginis excitand<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> grati<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>, neque enim co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odior ratio suppetit
    <lb/>varias co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>onstrandi verbo viri<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> mensuras) <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> ordinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>BEC</formula> conditi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>onibus nostri <rs type="biblio">Problematis</rs> satisfaciant, ut si fuerit <abbr>ex. g.</abbr> <del>[...]</del><formula>DC</formula> hor<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig>|</orig><reg>(</reg></choice>se<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice> rect<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/><formula>AC</formula><choice><orig>|</orig><reg>)</reg></choice> pars tertia, sit <formula>ED</formula> libr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig>|</orig><reg>(</reg></choice>se<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice> rect<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>AB</formula><choice><orig>|</orig><reg>)</reg></choice> pars dimidia, aut aliter vocumque;
    <lb/>dico i<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> futurum, ut si unitas illa <formula>CA</formula> non i<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> hor<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sit sed minuti, itemque 
  <pb facs="1063252" n="2"/> 
  <lb/><figure/> unitas <formula>BA</formula> non libr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sed minuti libralis, (part<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> libr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> 60.<hi rend="sup">m</hi> librale minutum
    <lb/>voco brevitatis grati<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>, ad exempl<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> minuti horarii); <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> proptere<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <formula>DC</formula> non hor<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sed
    <lb/>minuti pars tertia<del>[...]</del><add>;</add> <formula>DE</formula> non libr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sed minuti dimidium, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> sic de coeteris,
    <lb/><hi rend="u">analog<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> facta substitutione</hi>, se<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice> omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per mensur<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> librar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> horarum<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>que explicabantur eod<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> modo per mensuras minutor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> explicando; dico<supplied>,</supplied> in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>quam<supplied>,</supplied> <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> his positis, idem Curviline<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> iisd<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> nostris conditionibus satisfactu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum. Et id quid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> e<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> de caus<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>; quoni<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> conditiones Problematis nil sibi
    <lb/>velint aliud, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter relationem ordinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> cuiusvis ad aliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> ex abscissis,
    <lb/>puta ordinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>ED</formula> ad absciss<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <formula>CF</formula> (si quid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <formula>CF</formula> sit nimir<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> relativ<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> ad <formula>CA</formula>
    <lb/>tempus integr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, quando vi <formula>ED</formula> corpus agitur initi<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> motus) <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> quoni<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> eadem
    <lb/>illa relatio permanet, ut facil<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> apparet, eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> si pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dicto modo absolut<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
    <lb/>quantitates terminorum relationis immutentur, utique futur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> est, ut hoc
    <lb/>quoque casu conditionibus satis fiat. Porr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> constantes, si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Coordinata<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum relationem ingrediantur, perind<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> conflari oportet ex horis librisque
    <lb/>prim<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> casu, ac ex minutis secundo, aut <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> ea similiter datis, neque enim ali<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>unde possunt, ut proind<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> analogic<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> relation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> minim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> perturbent; et
    <lb/>quamvis, ut rect<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> notas, Curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <formula>BEC</formula> natura ponatur incognita, attamen
    <lb/>non et illud pariter verum erit, quor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> natura ignoratur, eorum quoque
    <lb/>passiones singulas <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> attributa latere; per h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c enim potius ad illa aditus
    <lb/>patet, atque ille elegantius censetur obscura patefacere, qui ex notis
    <lb/>ignoti passionibus eam usurpat, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> omnium maxim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> fuerit ad invo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>luti natur<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> explicand<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> accomodata. At alio quid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> pacto se res habe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>at necesse est, si conditiones ill<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> non ordinatar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> mod<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> regular<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ad
